No. 10-318. Kevin H. McKenna, Petitioner v. Nestle Purina PetCare Company. 562 U.S. 1037, 131 S. Ct. 568, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 8701.

178 L. Ed. 2d 427,

November 8, 2010.
